br />\n<br />\n我真係好想見到煲底相聚個一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:40:53.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n推"},{"pid":"3da0c2ed0c08ae1a1b328e6d9828847aaf1246ee","tid":1565752,"uid":290393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:41:06.000Z","msg":"我好同意, 多D支持, 少D指責."},{"pid":"5933dbe991b7f3133aebc35f6181bdd8faf561a6","tid":1565752,"uid":286589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"06f602809161535780a1e662905f0adf0ce8495a","tid":1565752,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:21:45.000Z","msg":"不指責係重點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:42:24.000Z","msg":"指責改為提醒，有錯都要提醒更正。<br />\n重來相信及尊重前線同勇武決定。我自問冇資格去指責前線。"},{"pid":"b30d1bf4b91bb87a29c678569a32ffc5cb52dd80","tid":1565752,"uid":215501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:42:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f33394670719094f0211a7382bb41eeb4e42b1dd","tid":1565752,"uid":290393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6a4e633b4105ef44f0a960899c6efacd623b2b07","tid":1565752,"uid":34266,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:37:39.000Z","msg":"係咁話唱歌就黎輸，好似雨革... <br />\n明明上星期先燒完中環站<br />\n<br />\n又話唱歌會輸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁你不如做樣行動出黎啦 你做得起d人自然會跟架啦，你睇人鏈依家中學生每隔幾日就整一條出黎<br />\n<br />\n講到尾就係，唔啱你心水，唔係按你所諗咁做就話會失敗，咁咪即係爭取緊話語權咪又係想做大台。 兄弟爬山咪得囉屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:43:05.000Z","msg":"係, 依家越來越有呢個情況, 無以前咁pure. 下下都要跟住指示做, 而指示係果層樓的樓主決定的"},{"pid":"e5c9bce946bcf74d3a3c1a8a1454643e9db794c3","tid":1565752,"uid":61105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6a4e633b4105ef44f0a960899c6efacd623b2b07","tid":1565752,"uid":34266,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:37:3